---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Shipping Policy">
    <main class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 pt-32">
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-gray-800/50 p-8 md:p-12">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8" 
                    style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #c084fc, #818cf8, #38bdf8);
                           -webkit-background-clip: text;
                           -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
                           background-clip: text;">
                    Shipping Policy
                </h1>

                <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
                    <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-6">
                        <section>
                            <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
                                This shipping policy outlines our practices regarding the delivery of products and services purchased through the Platform.
                            </p>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Service Delivery</h2>
                            
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 mb-6">
                                <p class="mb-4">
                                    FILLS AI CONSULTANCY primarily offers digital services and AI consulting solutions. Our "shipping" refers to the delivery of digital products and services:
                                </p>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3">
                                    <li>
                                        <strong class="text-white">Digital Products:</strong> Software, reports, documentation, and AI models are delivered electronically via email, cloud storage links, or through our platform within 24-48 hours of purchase.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong class="text-white">Consulting Services:</strong> Service delivery timelines are outlined in your service agreement and typically begin within 2-3 business days of contract signing.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong class="text-white">API Access:</strong> API keys and access credentials are provided immediately upon successful payment verification.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong class="text-white">Training Materials:</strong> Course materials and training documentation are provided on the scheduled start date of your program.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Physical Products</h2>
                            
                            <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-600/30 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
                                <p class="mb-4 text-blue-200">
                                    In cases where physical products (such as hardware, printed materials, or marketing collateral) are shipped:
                                </p>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 text-blue-100">
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Processing Time:</strong> Orders are processed within 2-3 business days
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Domestic Shipping (India):</strong> 5-7 business days via standard courier services
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Express Shipping:</strong> 2-3 business days (additional charges apply)
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Tracking:</strong> Tracking information will be provided via email once the order ships
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>

                            <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-600/30 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                                <p class="text-yellow-200 text-sm">
                                    <strong>Note:</strong> FILLS AI CONSULTANCY does not ship physical goods internationally at this time. All physical product deliveries are limited to addresses within India.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Shipping Charges</h2>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Digital Products & Services</h3>
                                    <p>
                                        <strong class="text-white">Free delivery</strong> - All digital products and services are delivered electronically at no additional cost.
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Physical Products</h3>
                                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                                        <li>Standard shipping: ₹50-150 depending on location and weight</li>
                                        <li>Express shipping: ₹200-500 depending on location and weight</li>
                                        <li>Free shipping on orders above ₹5,000</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                                        Shipping costs will be calculated and displayed at checkout before payment.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Delivery Timeline</h2>
                            
                            <div class="bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-600/30 rounded-lg p-6">
                                <table class="w-full">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr class="border-b border-purple-600/30">
                                            <th class="text-left py-3 text-purple-300">Service Type</th>
                                            <th class="text-left py-3 text-purple-300">Delivery Time</th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-purple-600/20">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="py-3">Digital Products</td>
                                            <td class="py-3">24-48 hours</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="py-3">API Access</td>
                                            <td class="py-3">Immediate</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="py-3">Consulting Services</td>
                                            <td class="py-3">2-3 business days to start</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="py-3">Physical Products (Standard)</td>
                                            <td class="py-3">5-7 business days</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="py-3">Physical Products (Express)</td>
                                            <td class="py-3">2-3 business days</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="py-3">Custom Development</td>
                                            <td class="py-3">As per project timeline</td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Order Tracking</h2>
                            
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">For Digital Products:</h3>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
                                    <li>You will receive a confirmation email upon purchase</li>
                                    <li>A second email with delivery details and access instructions within 24-48 hours</li>
                                    <li>Track your order status through your account dashboard on our platform</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 mt-6">For Physical Products:</h3>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                                    <li>You will receive order confirmation immediately after purchase</li>
                                    <li>Shipping confirmation with tracking number once the order ships</li>
                                    <li>Real-time tracking updates via SMS and email</li>
                                    <li>Delivery confirmation once the package is delivered</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Delivery Issues</h2>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Incorrect Address</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-2">
                                        Please ensure your shipping address is correct during checkout. We are not responsible for orders shipped to incorrect addresses provided by the customer.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                                        Address changes can be made within 24 hours of placing the order by contacting our support team.
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Failed Delivery Attempts</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-2">
                                        If delivery fails due to unavailability or incorrect contact information:
                                    </p>
                                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-sm">
                                        <li>The courier will attempt delivery 2-3 times</li>
                                        <li>You will receive notifications for each attempt</li>
                                        <li>If all attempts fail, the package will be returned to us</li>
                                        <li>Reshipment charges may apply</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>

                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Damaged or Lost Shipments</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-2">
                                        If your package arrives damaged or is lost in transit:
                                    </p>
                                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-sm">
                                        <li>Report the issue within 48 hours of delivery</li>
                                        <li>Provide photos of damaged packaging/items</li>
                                        <li>We will file a claim with the courier and arrange replacement</li>
                                        <li>No additional charges will be applied for replacement</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>

                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Delayed Deliveries</h3>
                                    <p>
                                        While we strive to meet all delivery timelines, delays may occur due to unforeseen circumstances such as weather, courier issues, or force majeure events. We will keep you informed of any significant delays.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Service Locations</h2>
                            
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Currently Shipping To:</h3>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                                    <li>
                                        <strong class="text-white">Digital Services:</strong> Available globally for clients worldwide
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong class="text-white">Physical Products:</strong> Currently shipping only within India
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong class="text-white">On-site Services:</strong> Available in Telangana and surrounding regions (additional travel charges may apply for distant locations)
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                                    We may not ship to certain remote areas. Please check serviceability by entering your PIN code at checkout.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Business Does Not Ship Goods</h2>
                            
                            <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-600/30 rounded-lg p-6">
                                <p class="text-blue-200 mb-3">
                                    <strong>Important Notice:</strong> FILLS AI CONSULTANCY primarily operates as a digital services and AI consulting company.
                                </p>
                                <p class="text-blue-100">
                                    If your business model does not involve shipping physical goods, this can be indicated during payment gateway setup. The majority of our transactions involve digital service delivery, software licensing, and consulting engagements that do not require traditional shipping.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Contact for Shipping Queries</h2>
                            <p class="mb-4">
                                For any questions about shipping or delivery status, please contact us:
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
                                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Company:</strong> FILLS AI CONSULTANCY</p>
                                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Address:</strong> Narsapur, Medak, Telangana, India</p>
                                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.fills.ai/" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">https://www.fills.ai/</a></p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-4">
                                    Customer Service Hours: Monday - Friday (9:00 AM - 6:00 PM IST)
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-gray-700">
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-center">
                                Last Updated: November 2024
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .prose p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .prose h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .prose h3 {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .prose a {
        transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .prose a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .prose ul, .prose ol {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .prose li {
        line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .prose table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .prose th,
    .prose td {
        text-align: left;
        padding: 0.75rem;
    }
</style>

